        <p>We have \(p = {@a1@}\). Substituting these values into the formula we find:</p>
        <p>\(\begin{aligned} R &amp;=5p^2\\ &amp;= (5)({@a1@}^2)\\ &amp;= (5)({@a1^2@})\\ &amp;= {@ta1@}. \end{aligned}\)</p>
